---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Illustration (placeholder) -->
      <div class="flex justify-center order-2 md:order-1">
        <img
          src={`${base}images/subsidy/problems-illust.jpg`}
          alt="窓の悩みを抱える女性のイメージ"
          loading="lazy"
          class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-xl"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Problems list -->
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <p class="text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold mb-2 tracking-wider">INTRODUCTION</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8">
          ずっと我慢している<br />「窓のお悩み」ありませんか？
        </h2>

        <ul class="space-y-0 divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M12 2v20M17 5l-5 3-5-3M17 19l-5-3-5 3M2 12h20M5 7l3 5-3 5M19 7l-3 5 3 5" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">冬の寒さ・夏の暑さ</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M12 2C12 2 6 10 6 15a6 6 0 0012 0c0-5-6-13-6-13z" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">毎朝ウンザリする窓の「結露・カビ」</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 2a6 6 0 00-3.742 10.69A1 1 0 017 13.5v.5a1 1 0 001 1h.5v1a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 001-1v-1h.5a1 1 0 001-1v-.5a1 1 0 01.742-.81A6 6 0 0010 2zM9 17a1 1 0 001 1h0a1 1 0 001-1v0H9v0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">年々高くなる「光熱費」</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-600">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                <polygon points="11 5 6 9 2 9 2 15 6 15 11 19 11 5" fill="currentColor" />
                <path d="M15.54 8.46a5 5 0 010 7.07" />
                <path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 010 14.14" />
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">気になる外の「騒音」</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-primary-100">
          <p class="text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            実はそれ、家の「窓（開口部）」を変えるだけでまとめて解決できるかもしれません。さらに今なら！<span class="font-bold text-primary-600">最大100万円の「補助金」</span>を使って、驚くほどお得にリフォームできる大チャンスです。ずっと抱えていた暮らしのストレス、この機会に賢く手放しませんか？
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
